This folder contains evidence of Linux file linking, inode inspection,
and disk usage analysis performed in the user's home directory.

## Tasks completed
- Created sample_data.txt with sample content
- Created a hard link (sample_hard.txt)
- Created a symbolic link (sample_soft.txt)
- Verified inode numbers using ls -i
- Inspected file metadata using stat
- Demonstrated disk usage with df -h and du -h
- Verified symbolic link deletion does not affect original file

## Key commands used
- echo
- ln
- ln -s
- ls -l
- ls -i
- stat
- rm
- df -h
- du -h
